    "Name": "Maxim APC",
    "Details": "Designed for LRM support, this updated version replaces the SRM-2s and TAG for a turret-mounted FarFire LRM-15. Originally produced by Maxim Transport Industries, before a series of scandals led to its closure in 3039, the fast and heavily armed Maxim quickly became the model example of a transport throughout the Inner Sphere. Still produced via different companies, the Maxim is still heavily used by many units as their principal APC. It has proven itself popular both to unit commanders, who respect its firepower, speed and ability to carry a full platoon of infantry, and to the troops it carries, who respect its roomy, comfortable infantry bay. \n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Biome Restrictions: This unit can not deploy in Lunar or Martian biomes due to using an ICE.</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 8/12 hexes / 240/360 meters.</color></b>\n\n<color=#ffcc00><b>Armor:</b> Ferro-Fibrous\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>       145     25\n<b>Left</b>         115     25\n<b>Right</b>       115     25\n<b>Rear</b>         80     25\n<b>Turret</b>      100     25\n\n<b>Total</b>      555    125</color>\n\n<color=#ff0000>Quirk: Rugged</color>",
